                    The California Board of Prison Terms



   Executive Officer, Board of Prison Terms

   The Executive Officer is responsible for the day to day operations of
   the Board. The Executive Officer also acts as the liaison on policy
   issues between the BPT and other state agencies, including the
   Department of Corrections, and is responsible for the implementation of
   the policies and procedures of the BPT.


